    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10010987>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Composite Digital Plate of Prosthechea sessiliflora (Orchidaceae). A. Habit. B. Detail of the new sympodium and its short inflorescence. C. Sympodium with fruits. D. Flower, frontal view. E. Side view of flower. F. Flora dissection: f1. Dorsal sepal; f2, f3. Lateral sepals; f4, f5. Lateral petals; f6. Lip. G. Lip in detail. H. Ovary and ventral view of column. I. Lateral view of ovary and column with lip. with lip. (Photos taken by ILM and digital plate designed by TLV)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10010987/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10010989>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Distribution map of Prosthechea sessiliflora (Orchidaceae). The red circles indicate the known records of the species, including historical records without current physical vouchers (lost materials) and the recent rediscoveries in the Cerrado domain." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10010989/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

